Summary: Simple linux tool for transfer mails from one mailserver to another mailserver
Home-page: https://github.com/amakeenk/mailtransfer
Author: Alexander Makeenkov
Author-email: whoami.tut@gmail.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: # mailtransfer
        Simple linux tool for transfer mails from one mailserver to another mailserver
        
        # Installation
        ```bash
        $ git clone https://github.com/amakeenk/mailtransfer
        $ cd mailtransfer
        $ python3 setup.py install
        ```
        # Usage
        ```bash
        $ mkdir ~/.mailtransfer
        $ cp mailtransfer-sample.cfg ~/.mailtransfer/mailtransfer.cfg
        $ chmod 0600 ~/.mailtransfer/mailtransfer.cfg
        $ vim mailtransfer.cfg
        $ mailtransfer start
        ```
        # Dependencies
        - colorama
        - configobj
        - daemon
        - emails
        - imap_tools
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
